data.description: This recently built residence is a true gem, offering a perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience. Situated on a corner lot, this property boasts a range of desirable features that will make you fall in love at first sight. Step inside this spacious 4-bedroom, 2-bathroom home, and be greeted by an inviting open floor plan. The high ceilings create an airy and expansive atmosphere, while the abundance of natural light floods the interior, giving it a warm and welcoming ambiance. The modern design and impeccable craftsmanship are evident throughout, showcasing the best of contemporary living. The well-appointed kitchen is a true delight for anyone, featuring sleek countertops, ample cabinetry, and stainless steel appliances. Whether you're preparing a quick breakfast or hosting a dinner party, this kitchen is equipped to handle it all. The kitchen seamlessly flows into the generous living room, creating a perfect space for entertaining guests or simply relaxing with family. Privacy and tranquility are guaranteed in the spacious master suite, complete with a en-suite bathroom and a large walk-in closet. The additional three bedrooms provide versatility and comfort, accommodating guests, a home office, or a hobby room with ease. With two bathrooms, getting ready in the morning will be a breeze for the entire family. One of the standout features of this home is the inside laundry area, offering convenience and functionality. The two-car garage provides additional storage space. Outside, the property is completely fenced, offering a secure and private backyard. Whether you desire a safe play area for children or a serene spot to enjoy the Florida sunshine, this fenced yard has you covered. The corner lot location adds to the overall appeal and provides an extra sense of space. Situated in the desirable West Port Reserve neighborhood, this home is conveniently located close to shopping centers, hospitals, and all the attractions that Port Orange has to offer. With its prime location, you'll have easy access to schools, parks, dining options, and entertainment venues, ensuring that you'll never have to travel far for your everyday needs. Square footage received from tax rolls. All information recorded in the MLS intended to be accurate but cannot be guaranteed.
